  - claude-code
version: 0.1.0
date-released: "2026-07-02"
abstract: >-
  EAIR is a research operating system for AI-driven science: multi-agent
  orchestration with preregistered decision rules, mandatory experiment
  bundles (treatment, baseline, ablation, controls under one protocol hash),
  adversarial cross-model audits, an evidence-gated design interrogation
  gate before GPU dispatch, and an append-only negative-results ledger.
